          "process_md": "***Registration Process:***\n**Step 01:** The applicant visits the [official website](https://jakega.jk.gov.in/index.html) and clicks the [notification](https://internshipjakega.jk.gov.in/) to apply. \n**Step 02:** Click on &quot;New User&quot; and fill in the basic details Name, Email ID, Mobile Number.\n**Step 03:** Generate the Password and enter the Captcha. \n<br>\n\n***Application Process:***\n**Step 01:** Log in to the profile and enter your email ID and password\n**Step 02:** Click the Apply internship scheme and enter the address, qualification, reference detail\n**Step 03:** Upload the domicile certificate, signature, resume, etc.\n**Step 04:** Click on the &quot;Submit&quot; button and your application number will be generated. \n<br>\n\n"
