        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The student should be studying at recognized universities in India.\n1. The student should have secured at least 60% marks in the last held degree or pursuing B.E/B.Tech/M.E/M.Tech (Computer Science &amp; Engineering (CSE)/Computer Science (CS)/ IT/ Electronics &amp; Communications (EC)/) M.Sc. (CS/IT/) MCA/DOEACC ‘B’ level. \n1. Students in the last semester or the final year will be eligible to apply. \n\n",
